            <p>THE SCHOOL OF VITAL SCIENCE&#44;<lb/></p>
            <p>Established 1871.	Victor B. Hall&#44; Founder.<lb/></p>
            <p>This School has three DEPARTMENTS&#44; with three courses of instruction in each.<lb/>  A program of students&#39; courses will be supplied on application.<lb/></p>
            <p>Our motto is Purity&#44; Peace&#44; Plenty.<lb/>  Our membership costs &#36;1.00 a year.<lb/></p>
            <p>We draw an exact line between all good and every evil.  We waste no time<lb/> opposing persons or systems&#44; but we set up the infallible standard of truth and win<lb/> them to it.  We uphold the sacredness of Life.<lb/></p>
            <p>We keep on file all progressive periodicals and obtain advertisements and sub&#45;<lb/>scriptions for them.  We have on our table the reports and constitutions of all God&#45;<lb/>honoring&#44; nonsectarian and liberal philosophical societies&#44; and to those persons who<lb/> write us their views &#40;enclosing stamp&#41;&#44; we send information of the societies we con&#45;<lb/>sider they would do well to join.<lb/></p>
            <p>Every good Word and Work Department.<lb/></p>
                <p>1121 Arch St Philadelphia&#44; 8 mo 28 1890<lb/></p>
            <p>Rev S. Morais&#44;<lb/>
                546 N<hi rend="underline">th</hi> 5<hi rend="underline">th</hi> St<lb/></p>
            <p>Friend&#58;&#45;&#45; I send two posters relating<lb/> to Strikes.  There may be in them some<lb/> points of aid.  <hi rend="underline">I believe I could raise funds for the<lb/> Jewish Alliance of America by lecturing in their behalf and I<lb/> am willing to do so</hi>.  I read the Jewish Exponent<lb/> regularly.  I am deeply interested in<lb/> the Hebrew people&#44; and <hi rend="underline">their mode of Life<lb/> and religion is mine</hi>.  I am very desirous<lb/> of seeing the Jewish Colonies thrive and<lb/> especially in Fruit growing.  I possess the<lb/> knowledge of causing fruit trees to have within<lb/> in them protective qualities against all insects.<lb/> without using any sprays of chemicals &#38;c.&#44; and also<lb/> I teach how to cause all fruit to become much<lb/> more gummy so that all fruit can be kept on the<lb/> trees till fully ripe and can be shipped long distances<lb/> without decay.  I want the people of One God benefited<lb/> by it.  See me.  Your Vital Friend. Victor B. Hall.<lb/></p>
            </body>
